                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    ğŸ“Š åˆ—è¡¨è§€å¯Ÿæ©Ÿ <span class="text-xs bg-gray-200 text-gray-600 px-2 py-1 rounded"></span>
